<title key="Food colourings, how to prepare seven in the course of the year">Willdu nu chochen mit den selbem varbem dy choch <date>noch des zeit Im Iar</date></title> 

<ab n="1" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.1"><opener>
<title key="White food colouring">WEiss</title> vindest du wal allbeg</opener> 
<instruction>Do machest du <alternative reason="dish"><dish en="puree" commodity="Q636056">gmues</dish> vnd <dish en="pastry" commodity="Q477248">gepachens</dish></alternative> von</instruction></ab> 

<ab n="2" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.2"> 
<title key="Red food colouring">Rot</title> 
<instruction>machstu von <ingredient commodity="Q0" en="unsolved">galilan per</ingredient> wann dy zeytig sein</instruction> so 
<instruction>press sy als ein <ingredient en="wine" commodity="Q282">wein</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>wenn sy nu geprest sein so seud sy</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>tue ein <ingredient en="honey" commodity="Q10987">honig</ingredient> dorin</instruction> <householdTip>so halcz du sew <time>ein gancz Iar</time></householdTip> 
<instruction>so machstu <alternative reason="dish"><dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">salssen</dish> vnd <dish en="puree" commodity="Q636056">gemues</dish></alternative> von</instruction></ab> <pb xml:id="W1_024r" n="024r"/> 

<ab n="3" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.3"> <opener>
<title key="Green food colouring">Gruen</title> das vindestu albeg wol</opener> 
<instruction>das machstu <alternative reason="ingredient">von <ingredient en="parsley" commodity="Q25284">petersil</ingredient> oder von anderm <ingredient en="herb" commodity="Q207123">kraut</ingredient></alternative></instruction> <instruction>do machstu <alternative reason="dish"><dish en="puree" commodity="Q636056">gmues</dish> vnd <dish en="pastry" commodity="Q477248">pachens</dish></alternative> von</instruction></ab> 

<ab n="4" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.4"> <opener>
<title key="Brown food colouring">Praun</title> machtu auch wol habem</opener> 
<instruction>das machstu von <ingredient en="sour cherry" commodity="Q68438267">weichseln</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>do machstu <dish en="puree" commodity="Q636056">gmues</dish> von wie du wild</instruction></ab> 

<ab n="5" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.5"> <opener>
<title key="Grey food colouring">Grab</title> das machstu auch wol habem</opener> 
<instruction>nym weysz vnd swarcz durich einander do wirt es grab von</instruction></ab> 

<ab n="6" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.6"> <opener>
<title key="Black food colouring">Swarcz</title> das machstu selber wol</opener> 
<instruction>das mach von <ingredient en="honey" commodity="Q10987">honig</ingredient> vnd von <ingredient en="gingerbread for sauce" commodity="Q1468150">leczlten</ingredient></instruction></ab> 

<ab n="7" type="recipe" subtype="subrecipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" xml:id="w1.209.sub.7"> <opener>
<title key="Yellow food colouring"><ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">Gel</ingredient></title> das ist auch guet</opener> 
<instruction>das machstu mit <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">saffran</ingredient> das des nicht zu vil sey oder es wuert rot</instruction></ab> <closer>etc.</closer></div></body></text></TEI>